		"description":{
			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>A coil of golden rope.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Wondrous Item</b><b>:</b> Common</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Property:</b></p> <p>This 100-foot-long rope has 100 hit points and can hold up to 2,500 pounds (roughly 10 Medium creatures and their gear).</p>\n<p class=\"subheading\"><b>Power (Minor Action)</b></p><p>The rope moves up to 10 squares along a horizontal or a vertical surface. As part of the same action, it can tie itself around an object to create a secure point for climbing. It can't tie itself to or otherwise affect a creature.</p><p>Anyone holding the rope can activate its power. On command, the rope unties itself as a minor action.</p>",
